page2.title: Help
page2.content: Where can I find an example quiz? . Click on the Test at the Top Right For more details, refer to the video tutorial. . How do I create an account? . Refer to the top right of the page and click Login and create an account from there. . How do I add flashcards? . Make sure to type in both a term and definition into the tool and press save. For more details, refer to the video tutorial. .
